flowchart LR
    SPEC[axme-spec\nschemas + OpenAPI]

    SPEC --> SDK[axme-sdk-*\nSDK tests]
    SPEC --> CONF[axme-conformance\nconformance suite]
    SPEC --> CP[axme-control-plane\nruntime]
    SPEC --> DOCS[axme-docs\ndocumentation]

    SDK --> E2E[E2E tests]
